            <h3>Python Developer</h3>
                <p>
                    Chango is seeking an energetic, motivated and intelligent software developer to join our engineering team. 
                </p>
                <p>
                    You will be working on an exciting product, contributing to different aspects of the system as required with room for growth into more senior positions. You will gain exposure to a high transaction “cloud scale” application that processes over 200,000 requests per second. You will work with Python and Django and get a taste of Erlang.
                <p>
                <p>
                    Chango is a successful, rapidly growing venture backed start-up, headquartered in Toronto, Canada, with growing offices in New York and San Francisco. Chango is changing the way advertisers buy display media, allowing advertisers to speak directly to consumers based on their recent searches on Google, Yahoo!, and Bing, among others.
                </p>
