                We are looking for an experienced Dev Ops / Systems Administrator to join our Infrastructure team, to be based in Toronto, Ontario office. The ideal candidate should be excited to join one of Canada’s leading start-ups and be motivated by the challenges of pushing the borders of web technology. As a point of reference, Twitter handles about 9000 tweets/second at peak!
